Class ContentTypeList

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.contenttype.base.ContentTypeList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JaxbObject

    public class ContentTypeList
extends Object
implements JaxbObject
    This is the container with all ContentTypeBeans. It allows to read them from an XML configuration via JAXB.

    1.0.0
    Author:
